kitchen tea
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a party to which guests bring gifts of kitchenware for a bride-to-be; also called a (kitchen) shower or kitchen evening.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
